TypeScript / Angular standards:
- Angular 21+ (zoneless + signals by default)
- Strict typing: no any, use interfaces over types when possible
- Prefer signals + functional components + inject()
- State: NgRx Signal Store or built-in signals
- Styling: TailwindCSS + Angular Material components
- Testing: Jasmine + Karma + Spectator
- Always lazy load routes & use OnPush change detection